data.description: Introducing a stunning property that boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 2035 sqft of living space. The floor plan is thoughtfully designed with a split plan and two additional rooms that provide flexibility. The open living room and dining area lead seamlessly to the modern kitchen, perfect for entertaining guests. The main bedroom is a true retreat with its generous size, two separate closets, stand-up shower, and tub. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home! Opportunity is knocking.
